Events.Text: You (Ben) want to organize a surprise party for your friend Alexis, who just got a degree in Engineering. Talk to your personal AI assistant. Maybe it can help? [instruction 1 of 6]
Hi I'm Ben I want to plan a party
Ideally, the thing should happen on Tuesday at the West Bay Venue, 10 pm, and you'd expect about 54 to show up. [instruction 2 of 6]

Scenario.UserTask: Follow the instructions and comments of the MTurk System bot (darker yellow boxes in the dialogue). Do not end the dialogue before the MTurk System bot (not the assistant) has told you to do so.
Scenario.WizardTask: Follow the flow charts and help the user plan a party.
